name: Uplink
description: This was going to be my CC3 map, but it doesn't meet my standards. Since I have already put alot of work into it I decided to finish it up and release it. Backstory: "We finally found a small landing stip to pick you up. It's on the rim of some canyon. The only problem is that the access to it is through a heavily infested bunker complex. Fight your way through and then radio us from the runway."
